channel.title: Help in makeing my server run plzzzzz!
channel.description:
the othre day i posted something about my server that i downloaded was not working in the login page to plzy the server!this is what he told me...You REALLY need to specify. First of all, it might not be client sided. have you tried:
•Changing the IP? •Making sure your server/source file is running? •Making sure there are no errors popping up when the source is running? •Making sure you are typing in the right log-in information? well im a noob and i dont know how to do this can u plz h elp me!!!step by step for each one plz?!?!?!
